b"@wolfowlvi I think $SBH is a clone of $MIK in so many ways. $KIRK is also a great retail story (my top holding). True, stock is up from $2 ->$18, but it's going to $30. Even more of a wholesale refurbishment of the company. Seeing the results now, but still in 3rd inning. #stocks #smallcaps"
